    <h1>Distance (Local Ranking)</h1>
    <p class="description">One of Google's three core local ranking factors &mdash; the physical proximity between searcher and business. Weighting increased permanently after the <strong>December 2021 Vicinity Update</strong>.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
          <span class="meta-author-role">Marketing Head &middot; theStacc</span>
        </div>
      </div>
